---
---
<section id="interests" class="interests-section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">What Makes Me, Me</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Interests & Passions</h2>

    <div class="interests-grid">

      <!-- Marvel -->
      <div class="interest-feature card">
        <div class="interest-icon-wrap" style="background: rgba(192,18,44,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(192,18,44,0.3);">
          <span class="interest-big-icon">⚡</span>
        </div>
        <div class="interest-content">
          <h3 class="interest-title">Marvel Universe</h3>
          <p class="interest-text">
            From Iron Man to the Multiverse Saga — I have watched every film, read the source
            comics, tracked every Easter egg, and can hold an hour-long conversation on why
            Tony Stark is the GOAT. Marvel isn't just entertainment; it's a masterclass in
            storytelling, sacrifice, and what it means to be a hero.
          </p>
          <div class="interest-tags">
            <span class="itag">Iron Man</span>
            <span class="itag">Avengers</span>
            <span class="itag">MCU Lore</span>
            <span class="itag">Comics</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Gaming -->
      <div class="interest-feature card">
        <div class="interest-icon-wrap" style="background: rgba(232,184,75,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.25);">
          <span class="interest-big-icon">🎮</span>
        </div>
        <div class="interest-content">
          <h3 class="interest-title">Gaming</h3>
          <p class="interest-text">
            Strategy, action, adventure — I play them all and I play them seriously. Gaming
            has taught me more about decision-making under pressure, pattern recognition, and
            creative problem-solving than any classroom. Also, my reaction time is genuinely
            superhuman at this point.
          </p>
          <div class="interest-tags">
            <span class="itag">Strategy</span>
            <span class="itag">Action RPG</span>
            <span class="itag">Competitive</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Small interest cards -->
      <div class="interest-small card">
        <span class="interest-emoji">📖</span>
        <h4 class="interest-small-title">Reading</h4>
        <p class="interest-small-text">History, science, and anything that changes the way I see the world. Currently reading biographies of great leaders.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="interest-small card">
        <span class="interest-emoji">🧠</span>
        <h4 class="interest-small-title">Debate & Rhetoric</h4>
        <p class="interest-small-text">The art of constructing an argument, anticipating the counter, and making your case heard. A lifelong pursuit.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="interest-small card">
        <span class="interest-emoji">🔭</span>
        <h4 class="interest-small-title">Science & Space</h4>
        <p class="interest-small-text">Physics, astronomy, the question of what lies beyond. The universe is the greatest story ever told.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="interest-small card">
        <span class="interest-emoji">🎵</span>
        <h4 class="interest-small-title">Music</h4>
        <p class="interest-small-text">Epic soundtracks, film scores, and the occasional banger. Hans Zimmer composed the soundtrack to my life.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.interests-section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.interests-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 1.25rem;
}

.interest-feature {
  grid-column: span 1;
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.interest-icon-wrap {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 56px; height: 56px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.interest-big-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; }
.interest-title {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.interest-text {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.interest-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }
.itag {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold);
  background: rgba(232,184,75,0.08);
  border: 1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.2);
  padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
}

.interest-small { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.interest-emoji { font-size: 1.5rem; }
.interest-small-title {
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0;
}
.interest-small-text {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .interests-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .interest-feature { flex-direction: column; }
}
</style>
